Lady Hawk followed Zardus and Battera back to the Alliance base. She
transformed to her half transformation and used her middle eye to scan the
base. "Autoguns online shields deactivated to allow entry, thick durable
walls, reinforced to take abuse. These alliance bots are nobodies fools when
it comes to security." The femm aproached a scanner and removed the sample
of DevilDuers DNA she'd borrowed. she held it in front of the scanner hoping
it would recognize the sample as the real thing and allow her access.

OOC it's your call Yanosh, does this mildly ingeneous plan work?
